Package: autoTDD
Title: Automated Trial Design Domains Creation
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Siddharth", "Lokineni", , "Sidhu871@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package automates the creation of Trial Design Domains (TA, TE, TI, TS) 
    for clinical trials based on data from ClinicalTrials.gov and user inputs. It supports 
    various trial designs including parallel, cross-over, single group, and factorial designs.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
DataFiles: inst/extdata/Trial_Summary.xlsx, inst/extdata/Als_file.xls
